cells.data:
-- partitionEithers :: [Either a b] -> ([a], [b])
on partitionEithers(xs)
    set ys to {}
    set zs to {}
    repeat with x in xs
        if isRight(x) then
            set end of zs to x
        else
            set end of ys to x
        end if
    end repeat
    Tuple(ys, zs)
end partitionEithers
